  "18:p18-b12": [{"version":1,"source":{"book":"dessin-scientifique","n":19,"page":18,"blockId":"p18-b12","caption":"Épure E 77 : projections verticale et horizontale d'un solide C-D-F, la ligne de terre π^V ch^V traversant la figure."},"units":"px","imageSize":{"width":720,"height":1010},"groundLine":{"a":{"x":20,"y":388},"b":{"x":702,"y":388}},"points":[{"id":"C","v":{"x":306,"y":483},"h":{"x":306,"y":483},"role":"vertex"},{"id":"D","v":{"x":539,"y":165},"h":{"x":539,"y":450},"role":"vertex"},{"id":"E","v":{"x":539,"y":375},"h":{"x":539,"y":782},"role":"vertex"},{"id":"F","v":{"x":608,"y":468},"h":{"x":608,"y":505},"role":"vertex"}],"segments":[{"from":"C","to":"D","view":"v"},{"from":"D","to":"F","view":"v"},{"from":"C","to":"F","view":"v"},{"from":"C","to":"E","view":"v"},{"from":"E","to":"F","view":"v"},{"from":"D","to":"E","view":"v"}],"operation":{"kind":"point_projection","points":["C","D","E","F"]},"notes":["Tétraèdre C-D-E-F lifté par point_projection ; la ligne de terre traverse la figure (C, E, F sous la LT ; D au-dessus).","C : projections verticale et horizontale confondues en un seul point (306,483) — v==h, point dont les deux vues coïncident, pas une pile ambiguë.","D et E sont sur un même rappel de profil (la verticale D^V-B^V à x≈533 et la verticale D^H-E^H à x≈543 sont le même rappel, ~9px de jeu de tracé) ; abscisse harmonisée à x=539 pour les deux.","Ignorés (construction/perçage) : A^V/O^V sur la mince ligne C-A ; B^V trace sous E sur la verticale prolongée ; I sur l'arête C-D ; leurs rabattus C^H_R, E^H_R."]}],
